</figure>
<h3><a href="/beijing_treaty/en/">WIPO's Beijing Treaty Enters into Force: Begins Helping Actors and other Performers</a></h3>
</div>
</div>
<div class="content cols cols--three line">
<h2 id="initiatives">WIPO initiatives</h2>
<div class="col">
<h3>WIPO for Creators</h3>
<p>This joint initiative between WIPO and the <a href="http://musicrightsawareness.org/">Music Rights Awareness Foundation</a> supports creators around the world in ensuring they are fairly remunerated for their work by increasing knowledge and awareness of their IP rights. <br />Charter&nbsp;<a href="/export/sites/www/wipoforcreators/en/docs/charter_creators.pdf" title="Charter of WIPO for Creators"><img src="/export/sites/www/shared/images/icon/new/pdf.svg" alt="PDF, Making the Most of the Madrid System" /></a> | <a href="/pressroom/en/articles/2020/article_0016.html">Press Release</a></p>
</div>
<div class="col">
<h3>Accessible Books Consortium</h3>
<p>The <a href="https://www.accessiblebooksconsortium.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Accessible Books Consortium </a> (ABC) aims to increase the number of books worldwide in accessible formats – such as braille, audio and large print – and to make them available to people who are blind, have low vision or are otherwise print disabled.</p>
</div>
<div class="col">
<div class="box">
<h3 class="box__header">Marrakesh VIP Treaty</h3>
<p>The <a href="/marrakesh_treaty/en/">Marrakesh Treaty</a> underpins the ABC’s work, making the production and international transfer of specially-adapted books for people with blindness or visual impairments easier.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
