<h3 class="box__header">WIPO Connect</h3>
<ul class="box__list">
<li><a href="/global_ip/en/activities/wipo_connect/">WIPO Connect</a> is an IT system for CMOs to facilitate the collective management of copyrights.</li>
</ul>
</div>
